 ja magistriõpe", "en": "integrated bachelor's and master's studies"}], "hours": {"lecture": 10, "practice": 30, "seminar": 0, "colloquium": 0, "web_learning": 0, "independent_work": 38, "individual_work": 0, "internship": 0}, "prerequisites": [{"required": true, "uuid": "62901d09-3d45-ffd9-06b8-8df341b867b7", "code": "AR00.00.016", "title": {"en": "Fundamentals of Diagnostics", "et": "Diagnostika alused"}, "credits": 17, "state": {"code": "confirmed", "et": "Kinnitatud", "en": "confirmed"}, "last_update": "2024-02-05T11:04:36"}], "is_enlight_course": false}, "overview": {"study_languages": [{"code": "et", "et": "eesti keel", "en": "Estonian"}], "description": {"en": "Diagnostic and treatment principles, methods and tactics of general and abdominal surgical diseases. The course is a part of the subject \"Surgery\" (12 ECTS).", "et": "Üld- ja abdominaalkirurgiliste haiguste diagnoosimise ja ravi printsiibid, metoodika ja taktika. Antud aine moodustab ühe osa õppeainest \"Kirurgia\" (12 EAP)"}, "objectives": [{"en": "To teach the epidemiology, etiology, clinical picture, possible complications, diagnostics, treatment principles, prognosis and prophylaxis of common surgical diseases of the abdominal cavity.", "et": "Õpetada kõhuõõne kirurgiliste haiguste epidemioloogiat, kliinilist pilti, võimalikke komplikatsioone, diagnostikat, ravi, prognoosimist ja profülaktikat."}], "learning_outcomes": [{"en": "After completing the course the student knows ", "et": "Õppe tulemusena peavad üliõpilased teadma:"}, {"en": "1) the epidemiology, etiology,pathogenesis and prophylaxis of more frequent surgical diseases;", "et": "1) sagedamini esinevate kirurgiliste haiguste epidemioloogiat, etioloogiat, patogeneesi ja profülaktikat ;"}, {"en": "2) the clinical picture and possible complications of surgical diseases;", "et": "2) nende haiguste kliinilist pilti ja võimalikke tüsistusi;"}, {"en": "3) contemporary clinical, laboratory and instrumental methods  of patient investigation;", "et": "3) teadma kaasaegseid kliinilise laboratoorseid ja instrumentaalseid haigete uurimise meetodeid;"}, {"en": "4) treatment methods, incl operative treatment, and indications for their usage.", "et": "4) ravimeetodeid, sh operatiivne ravi, ja nende kasutamise näidustusi."}, {"en": "The student is able to", "et": "Õppe tulemusena peavad üliõpilased oskama:"}, {"en": "1) take the anamnesis, carry out clinical examinations of a surgical patient and to analyse the results of general clinical tests;", "et": "1) võtta anamneesi, läbi viima kliinilisi uurimisi kirurgilistel haigetel ja analüüsima üldkliinilise uurimise tulemusi;"}, {"en": "2) draw up a plan for laboratory and instrumental examinations and analyse their results;", "et": "2) koostada plaani laboratoorseteks ja instrumentaalseteks uuringuteks ning analüüsima laboratoorsete ja instrumentaalsete analüüside tulemusi;"}, {"en": "3) make clinical diagnosis, explain it on the basis of differential diagnosis;", "et": "3) formuleerima kliinilist diagnoosi, seda põhjendama diferentsiaaldiagnoosi põhjal;"}, {"en": "4) determine indications for conservative or surgical treatment;", "et": "4) formuleerima näidustused konservatiivseks ja operatiivseks raviks;"}, {"en": "5) choose a method for operative treatment according to pathological changes.", "et": "5) oskama valida operatiivse ravi meetodit vastavalt haiguslikele muutustele."}], "notes": {}}, "grading": {"independent_work": {}, "independent_work_assessments": [{"work_type": {"code": "written", "et": "Kirjalik lõpphindamine", "en": "final written assessment"}, "description": {"et": "Kirjalik eksam, osa koondeksamist Kirurgia"}}], "grade_preconditions": {"et": "Praktikumidest osavõtt"}, "grade_evaluation": {"et": "1 osa komplekseksamist \"Kirurgia\""}, "debt_elimination": {"et": "referaat puudutud praktikumi teema kohta, maksimaalselt 2 puudumist praktikumidest."}, "assessment_scale": {"code": "pass", "et": "Eristamata (arv, m.arv, mi)", "en": "non-differentiated (p